title: [PS3] ZER0 4.55 CFW V1.00-CEX + multiMAN-ReActPSN
description:
ZER0 4.55 CFW V1.00-CEX: From a New Team of some familiar names .... 
Here comes the latest Standard-CEX 4.55 CFW from a familiar face with a new team, following the recent 4.55 official ps3 update. CFW Developer Habib (aka smhabib) releases this new CFW as he is now apart of a team of developers, called "ZER0", we are not sure of all the the developers of this new team but we have some ideas after reading this release quote by Habib. Also added latest multiMAN v4.55 and reActPSN v3.12
